<ul>
    <li>2-hand placement is allowed</li>
    <li>Piece becomes active as soon as picked up</li>
    <li>Active piece goes anywhere, but cannot touch table</li>
    <li>May hold base with 1 hand</li>
    <li>May use active piece to move other pieces</li>
    <li>Must place pieces one at a time</li>
    <li>If the active piece falls, it may picked it up again, but only if it fell immediately upon placement</li>
    <li>Any time a piece falls off the structure and touches the table it becomes a fallen piece, and is set aside</li>
</ul>

