@*hometown
---
2-6
goal: most fans, bonus for tallest
end: a player has 5+ fallen pieces, finish current round so all players take same number of turns
scoring: match active piece color/shape
    -1 per fallen piece
    tallest 3 structures get 5/3/1 bonus fans
    score for hometown may not be negative (i.e. do not lose fans from previous rounds)

deal 4 per player
turns proceed 1 at a time
1. AP chooses 2 cards, gives them to next player
2. that player chooses 1 card and hands back the other
3. both players add the pieces
4. +1 fan for each matching color or shape as the active piece
5. refill hand to 4


Amsterdam
---
3-6
goal: tallest
end: a player is eliminated - has 2+ fallen pieces
    or cards run out
scoring: 3 fans to tallest structure, 2 fans to other non-eliminated players

deal 3 per player
turns are simultaneous
1. choose 1 card then all reveal
2. determine who played strongest card: highest card number
    ties: orange > blue > green > gray
3. winner gathers all cards, distributes 1 card to each player
4. all players find & add

